ation has invested over $66 billion in community colleges, providing over=
 19 million Pell scholarships to students attending community colleges; t=
his funding to community colleges represents over one-third of all Pell g=
rants. To continue improving and expanding these important investments, t=
he Administration will soon announce selected pilot sites who for the fir=
