t programs help high school students earn better grades and increase thei=
r likelihood of college enrollment, persistence and completion. In additi=
on, to further strengthen community colleges, particularly for traditiona=
l underrepresented students, this Administration has invested $1.6 billio=
n in Title III and Title V programs.=20
