ion and partnered with Bridgestone Tire Company to develop a new mechatro=
nics training facility on-site at Bridgestone in Smyrna, TN. In addition =
to contributing to curriculum development, Bridgestone has contributed ov=
er $4 million towards renovations and equipment.

o "_Piedmont Technical College (PTC) (SC)._" As part of a consortium cons=
isting of 10 of the 16 public, two-year colleges in South Carolina and fu=
