o "_Alpena Community College (ACC) (MI)_": ACC received $2.8 million to i=
mplement the Sustainable Solutions for Northeast Michigan: Green Jobs and=
 Clean Energy project to build a statewide energy partnership network, wh=
ich included the Michigan National Guard and DTE Energy and Consumers Ene=
rgy, the two largest energy employers in Michigan as well as the state wo=
rkforce development board. This partnership network designed and implemen=
ted a Gas Energy Bootcamp, targeting unemployed people and returning vete=
